natlang.rdg.model
Class RSTreeNodeData

java.lang.Object
  natlang.rdg.model.RSTreeNodeData
public class RSTreeNodeData
extends java.lang.Object

RSTreeNodeData holds the data of a treenode in a RS Dependency tree, e.g. its category or its pos-tag, its relation to its parent node, its root, perhaps its surface form (word), and perhaps its index. It also contains a boolean stating whether another such node exists in the dependency graph
